00:00:00,840 --> 00:00:03,910
Reflecting on where we've encountered
invisible interfaces is difficult,

2
00:00:03,910 --> 00:00:06,140
because they were invisible.

3
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:09,550
What makes them so good is the fact
that we didn't have to notice them.

4
00:00:09,550 --> 00:00:10,470
But give it a try anyway.

5
00:00:10,470 --> 00:00:12,930
Try to think of a time where you
picked up a new interface for

6
00:00:12,930 --> 00:00:14,300
the very first time and

7
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,760
immediately knew exactly how to use it
to accomplish the task you had in mind.

